\begin_layout Enumerate
Desigualdad triangular:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\forall f\in{\cal L}^{1}(\mu),\left|\int f\,d\mu\right|\leq\int|f|d\mu
\]

\end_inset

Si 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|\int f\,d\mu\right|=0$
\end_inset

