\begin_inset Formula $\int2g\,d\mu=\int\liminf_{n}(2g-|f-f_{n}|)d\mu\leq\liminf_{n}\int(2g-|f-f_{n}|)d\mu=\int2g\,d\mu-\limsup_{n}\int|f-f_{n}|$
